that same question again.

1395
01:39:27,441 --> 01:39:31,002
''Are you living or are you existing?''

1396
01:39:31,212 --> 01:39:36,081
lt's funny what your mind
goes back to when you're grieving.

1397
01:39:36,717 --> 01:39:41,245
